Fast rising music act, Kingsley Anche Clement aka Chrocboy has concluded arrangements to launch his first single ‘talk’ on June 25. The Kaduna-born 26-year-old UNIJOS Mathematics graduate started playing music as a young boy in the church. He moved to Lagos in 2020 to pursue his musical career. Chrocboy, who grew up in Michika, Adamawa State, said on his instragam handle @chrocboyofficial, that the single Is to establish himself as a musician worthy of huge fan base within and outside the country.